Any ideas what the red X indicator means? FF.png
Looking at the individual jobs all of them are either yellow (running) or green it seems :thinking:
https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/89783
if you click on the :cross_mark: there will be a popup with the list of CI checks
Ah so its just bors not noticing the ci failure right away? (I have no idea how bors parses the ci results tbh)

the failing CI test triggers a followup task (which generates the comment, I assume). From the timestamps it looks like it took two minutes between the failure and the comment being generated, so you probably looked at it during that gap.
